      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935167
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253efd",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253efe",
      "text": " [Xが信じるYを信じろ]シリーズ、全部良い感じに見える",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253eff",
      "text": " \t[お前が信じるお前を信じろ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253f00",
      "text": " \t[俺が信じるお前を信じろ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253f01",
      "text": " \t[俺が信じる俺を信じろ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253f02",
      "text": " \t[お前が信じる俺を信じろ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253f03",
      "text": " \t俺俺だけ宙に浮いてる感じがしてダメだな",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253f04",
      "text": "  \t根拠が接続されておらずコミュニケーションになってない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253f05",
      "text": " \t[お前が信じるお前を信じろ]って言われても信じられないけど、[俺が信じるお前を信じろ]って言われたら信じられるタイプ、居そう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253f06",
      "text": " \t\t他人に依存するリスクがあるけど",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778935152,
      "updated": 1778935152
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08656f0000000000253f07",
